%% 3.1.9 Guardian Management — sequence (layered)
%% Actor > UI > Controller > Service > Repository > Database

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Actor as Admin or Staff
    participant UI as UI (/guardians-manage)
    participant UC as Controller (UserController)
    participant US as Service (UserService)
    participant Repo as Repository (IRepository User)
    participant DB as Database (SQL Server)

    Actor->>UI: Open Guardian Management
    UI->>UC: GET /api/User/Search?role=guardian&keyword=...
    UC->>US: SearchUserAsync
    US->>Repo: Query users
    Repo->>DB: SELECT
    US-->>UC: list (Name, Phone, ...)
    UC-->>UI: 200 — grid

    Note over UI,DB: Linked student count — GET /api/Student/GetByGuardian/{id} or aggregate

    Actor->>UI: Eye — View household
    UI->>UC: GET /api/User/Get/{id}
    UC->>US: GetUserByIdAsync
    US->>Repo: Load user + role
    Repo->>DB: SELECT
    UC-->>UI: 200 — guardian profile + children list (extra calls as needed)

    Actor->>UI: Block Account → Confirm + optional reason
    UI->>UC: DELETE /api/User/Delete/{id} (soft-disable guardian)
    UC->>US: DeleteUserAsync — sets Status DISABLED
    US->>Repo: Update user status
    Repo->>DB: UPDATE Users
    DB-->>Repo: OK
    UC-->>UI: 200
    UI->>UI: Row label Banned
    UI-->>Actor: Done

    Note over Actor,DB: BR09 — JWT trên mobile: không còn hợp lệ sau khi khóa nếu có token blacklist hoặc mọi API kiểm tra AccountStatus; JWT cũ có thể sống đến khi hết hạn nếu chưa có revoke server-side.
